  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Are You Ready To \"Winch It Out\"?</strong></h2>This is a <strong>Hardcore, Physics-based, Driving Platformer</strong>. If you're tired of the same old <strong>Gas-and-Go</strong> 2D driving games and want a more <strong>Challenging</strong> experience, this one's for you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/4fc8952aa7c39b44114fd32243eb7379.poster.avif?t=1729664029\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/4fc8952aa7c39b44114fd32243eb7379.webm?t=1729664029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/4fc8952aa7c39b44114fd32243eb7379.mp4?t=1729664029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Diverse Environments:</strong></h2> Navigate through <strong>Deserts</strong>, <strong>Forests</strong>, <strong>Mountains</strong>, <strong>Dungeons</strong>, and more, Each biome has its own unique set of physics-based challenges, requiring you to think and strategize to navigate each terrain.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/c742523a123380cf67d14dd9a73af0a0.poster.avif?t=1729664029\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/c742523a123380cf67d14dd9a73af0a0.webm?t=1729664029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/c742523a123380cf67d14dd9a73af0a0.mp4?t=1729664029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Manual Transmission</strong></h2>Using a <strong>Manual Gear Shifter</strong> you'll have full control over <strong>Power</strong> and <strong>Speed</strong> of your car. Each Car comes with a special set of abilities designed to solve specific challenges. From your trusty <strong>Winch</strong> to <strong>Boost</strong>, <strong>Dash</strong>, <strong>Chain</strong>, <strong>Glide</strong>, and everything in between!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/5f3d0566eaedff9a315b90f177c36598.poster.avif?t=1729664029\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/5f3d0566eaedff9a315b90f177c36598.webm?t=1729664029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/5f3d0566eaedff9a315b90f177c36598.mp4?t=1729664029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grounded</strong></h2>There are <strong>NO</strong> backflips or mid-air car rotations because it's weird!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Developer's Note:</strong></h2>Hey there! I'm the solo developer behind this project and a fan of physics-based driving games, Mudrunner, Trials, and the old motocross games from the Flash era (good old times!)<br>I've been waiting to see more games in this genre. So I decided to create one myself with that <strong>Weighty </strong>and <strong>Off-Roady</strong> feeling I’ve been craving. I hope it fills the gap for you too!<br><br>Drop me a message on Steam anytime!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Are You Ready To \"Winch It Out\"?</strong></h2>This is a <strong>Hardcore, Physics-based, Driving Platformer</strong>. If you're tired of the same old <strong>Gas-and-Go</strong> 2D driving games and want a more <strong>Challenging</strong> experience, this one's for you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/4fc8952aa7c39b44114fd32243eb7379.poster.avif?t=1729664029\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/4fc8952aa7c39b44114fd32243eb7379.webm?t=1729664029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/4fc8952aa7c39b44114fd32243eb7379.mp4?t=1729664029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Diverse Environments:</strong></h2> Navigate through <strong>Deserts</strong>, <strong>Forests</strong>, <strong>Mountains</strong>, <strong>Dungeons</strong>, and more, Each biome has its own unique set of physics-based challenges, requiring you to think and strategize to navigate each terrain.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/c742523a123380cf67d14dd9a73af0a0.poster.avif?t=1729664029\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/c742523a123380cf67d14dd9a73af0a0.webm?t=1729664029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/c742523a123380cf67d14dd9a73af0a0.mp4?t=1729664029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Manual Transmission</strong></h2>Using a <strong>Manual Gear Shifter</strong> you'll have full control over <strong>Power</strong> and <strong>Speed</strong> of your car. Each Car comes with a special set of abilities designed to solve specific challenges. From your trusty <strong>Winch</strong> to <strong>Boost</strong>, <strong>Dash</strong>, <strong>Chain</strong>, <strong>Glide</strong>, and everything in between!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/5f3d0566eaedff9a315b90f177c36598.poster.avif?t=1729664029\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/5f3d0566eaedff9a315b90f177c36598.webm?t=1729664029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956360/extras/5f3d0566eaedff9a315b90f177c36598.mp4?t=1729664029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grounded</strong></h2>There are <strong>NO</strong> backflips or mid-air car rotations because it's weird!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Developer's Note:</strong></h2>Hey there! I'm the solo developer behind this project and a fan of physics-based driving games, Mudrunner, Trials, and the old motocross games from the Flash era (good old times!)<br>I've been waiting to see more games in this genre. So I decided to create one myself with that <strong>Weighty </strong>and <strong>Off-Roady</strong> feeling I’ve been craving. I hope it fills the gap for you too!<br><br>Drop me a message on Steam anytime!",
